    <div class="col s12 m12">
        <div class="card">
      	   <div class="card-content center-align">
                <h5>Prayer - insight</h5>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Distinctio provident ratione, sapiente cupiditate nihil commodi, eius perspiciatis nostrum dicta a minima ex vero doloremque assumenda voluptates illum ea odit unde?</p>
                
